import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { Box, Grid, Card, CardContent, Typography, Paper, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Chip, CircularProgress } from '@mui/material'; import { People, Assignment, Dashboard, TrendingUp, Email } from '@mui/icons-material'; import { toast } from 'react-toastify'; import axios from 'axios'; const DashboardOverview = () => { const [overview, setOverview] = useState(null); const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true); useEffect(() => { fetchOverview(); }, []); const fetchOverview = async () => { try { const response = await axios.get('/api/admin/dashboard/overview'); setOverview(response.data); } catch (error) { console.error('Fetch overview error:', error); toast.error('Failed to fetch dashboard overview'); } finally { setLoading(false); } }; if (loading) { return ( ); } if (!overview) { return ( Failed to load dashboard overview. Please try again. ); } const { roleStats, recentAssignments, systemStats } = overview; return ( Dashboard Overview {/* System Statistics */} Total Users {systemStats?.totalUsers || 0} Total Assignments {systemStats?.totalAssignments || 0} Total Candidates {systemStats?.totalCandidates || 0} Active Roles {Object.keys(roleStats || {}).length} {/* Role Statistics */} {roleStats && Object.entries(roleStats).map(([role, stats]) => ( {role} Statistics Total {stats.total} Active {stats.active} Pending {stats.pending} Registered {stats.registered} ))} {/* Recent Assignments */} Recent Role Assignments Email Role Status Invited By Date {recentAssignments?.map((assignment) => ( {assignment.email} {assignment.invitedBy?.name || 'N/A'} {new Date(assignment.invitedAt).toLocaleDateString()} ))}
{(!recentAssignments || recentAssignments.length === 0) && ( No recent role assignments )} ); }; export default DashboardOverview;
